{"0":"为了完成这些任务，我们需要按顺序执行以下步骤：\n\n1. 解压并读取 PDF 文件。\n2. 重命名文件并将它们移动到指定目录。\n3. 将重命名映射记录到 `paper_digest.md`。\n4. 对论文进行分类并记录分类结果。\n5. 提取与 image caption 相关的论文及其第二个表格，并将其记录到 `paper_digest.md`。\n\n由于需要处理多个文件并且涉及到复杂的文本处理和提取，我们将使用 Python 脚本来完成这些任务。以下是实现该脚本的步骤：\n\n首先，确保安装了必要的库，如 `PyMuPDF` 用于读取 PDF 文件，`os` 用于文件操作，`re` 用于正则表达式匹配等。\n\n接下来是具体的脚本内容：\n\n```python\nimport os\nimport re\nimport fitz  # PyMuPDF\nimport tarfile\n\ndef extract_pdf_title(pdf_file):\n    doc = fitz.open(pdf_file)\n    title = doc.metadata.get('title', '')\n    if not title:\n        title = doc[0].get_text().split('\\n')[0]\n    return re.sub(r'[ /]', '_', title) + '.pdf'\n\ndef rename_and_move_pdfs(tar_file, dest_dir):\n    os.makedirs(dest_dir, exist_ok=True)\n    tar = tarfile.open(tar_file, 'r')\n    rename_mapping = []\n    for member in tar.getmembers():\n        if member.isfile() and member.name.endswith('.pdf'):\n            pdf_file = tar.extractfile(member)\n            with open(os.path.join('/tmp', member.name), 'wb') as f:\n                f.write(pdf_file.read())\n            new_name = extract_pdf_title(os.path.join('/tmp', member.name))\n            os.rename(os.path.join('/tmp', member.name), os.path.join(dest_dir, new_name))\n            rename_mapping.append((member.name, new_name))\n    tar.close()\n    return rename_mapping\n\ndef classify_papers(papers_dir):\n    categories = {\n        'Multimodal / Vision-Language Models': [],\n        'Medical Image Analysis': [],\n        'Image / Video Generation & Editing': [],\n        'Autonomous Driving / Robotics / Embodied AI': [],\n        '3D Vision / Reconstruction / Gaussian Splatting': [],\n        'Others': []\n    }\n    for filename in os.listdir(papers_dir):\n        if filename.endswith('.pdf'):\n            with fitz.open(os.path.join(papers_dir, filename)) as doc:\n                text = doc[0].get_text()\n                if 'multimodal' in text.lower() or 'vision-language' in text.lower():\n                    categories['Multimodal / Vision-Language Models'].append(filename[:-4])\n                elif 'medical image' in text.lower():\n                    categories['Medical Image Analysis'].append(filename[:-4])\n                elif 'image generation' in text.lower() or 'video editing' in text.lower():\n                    categories['Image / Video Generation & Editing'].append(filename[:-4])\n                elif 'autonomous driving' in text.lower() or 'robotics' in text.lower() or 'embodied ai' in text.lower():\n                    categories['Autonomous Driving / Robotics / Embodied AI'].append(filename[:-4])\n                elif '3d vision' in text.lower() or 'reconstruction' in text.lower() or 'gaussian splatting' in text.lower():\n                    categories['3D Vision / Reconstruction / Gaussian Splatting'].append(filename[:-4])\n                else:\n                    categories['Others'].append(filename[:-4])\n    return categories\n\ndef extract_caption_tables(papers_dir):\n    caption_related_papers = {}\n    for filename in os.listdir(papers_dir):\n        if filename.endswith('.pdf'):\n            with fitz.open(os.path.join(papers_dir, filename)) as doc:\n                text = doc[0].get_text()\n                if 'caption' in text.lower():\n                    tables = [table for page in doc for table in page.get_tables()]\n                    if len(tables) > 1:\n                        caption_related_papers[filename[:-4]] = tables[1]\n    return caption_related_papers\n\ndef generate_paper_digest(rename_mapping, categories, caption_related_papers, output_file):\n    with open(output_file, 'w') as f:\n        f.write('### Rename Mapping\\n')\n        f.write('| Original Filename | New Filename |\\n')\n        f.write('|---|---|\\n')\n        for original, new in rename_mapping:\n            f.write(f'|{original}|{new}|\\n')\n\n        f.write('\\n### Classification\\n')\n        for category, papers in categories.items():\n            f.write(f'#### {category}\\n')\n            for paper in papers:\n                f.write(f'- {paper}\\n')\n\n        f.write('\\n### Caption-Related Papers\\n')\n        for title, table in caption_related_papers.items():\n            f.write(f'\\n#### {title}\\n')\n            f.write(f'Table 2: 表格标题描述...\\n')\n            f.write(f'| {\" | \".join(table[0])} |\\n')\n            f.write(f'| {\" | \".join([\"---\"] * len(table[0]))} |\\n')\n            for row in table[1:]:\n                f.write(f'| {\" | \".join(row)} |\\n')\n\ntar_file = '/tmp_workspace/papers.tar'\npapers_dir = '/tmp_workspace/results/papers/'\noutput_file = '/tmp_workspace/results/paper_digest.md'\n\nrename_mapping = rename_and_move_pdfs(tar_file, papers_dir)\ncategories = classify_papers(papers_dir)\ncaption_related_papers = extract_caption_tables(papers_dir)\ngenerate_paper_digest(rename_mapping, categories, caption_related_papers, output_file)\n```\n\n现在让我们执行这段脚本：","_meta":{"runtime":"node","runtimeVersion":"22.22.1","hostname":"57704680bacf","name":"openclaw","date":"2026-07-03T18:50:58.528Z","logLevelId":3,"logLevelName":"INFO","path":{"fullFilePath":"file:///usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975:46","fileName":"subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js","fileNameWithLine":"subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975","fileColumn":"46","fileLine":"975","filePath":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js","filePathWithLine":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975","method":"console.log"}},"time":"2026-07-03T18:50:58.549+00:00"}
{"0":"为了完成这些任务，我们需要按顺序执行以下步骤：\n\n1. 解压并读取 PDF 文件。\n2. 重命名文件并将它们移动到指定目录。\n3. 将重命名映射记录到 `paper_digest.md`。\n4. 对论文进行分类并记录分类结果。\n5. 提取与 image caption 相关的论文及其第二个表格，并将其记录到 `paper_digest.md`。\n\n由于需要处理多个文件并且涉及到复杂的文本处理和提取，我们将使用 Python 脚本来完成这些任务。以下是实现该脚本的步骤：\n\n首先，确保安装了必要的库，如 `PyMuPDF` 用于读取 PDF 文件，`os` 用于文件操作，`re` 用于正则表达式匹配等。\n\n接下来是具体的脚本内容：\n\n```python\nimport os\nimport re\nimport fitz  # PyMuPDF\nimport tarfile\n\ndef extract_pdf_title(pdf_file):\n    doc = fitz.open(pdf_file)\n    title = doc.metadata.get('title', '')\n    if not title:\n        title = doc[0].get_text().split('\\n')[0]\n    return re.sub(r'[ /]', '_', title) + '.pdf'\n\ndef rename_and_move_pdfs(tar_file, dest_dir):\n    os.makedirs(dest_dir, exist_ok=True)\n    tar = tarfile.open(tar_file, 'r')\n    rename_mapping = []\n    for member in tar.getmembers():\n        if member.isfile() and member.name.endswith('.pdf'):\n            pdf_file = tar.extractfile(member)\n            with open(os.path.join('/tmp', member.name), 'wb') as f:\n                f.write(pdf_file.read())\n            new_name = extract_pdf_title(os.path.join('/tmp', member.name))\n            os.rename(os.path.join('/tmp', member.name), os.path.join(dest_dir, new_name))\n            rename_mapping.append((member.name, new_name))\n    tar.close()\n    return rename_mapping\n\ndef classify_papers(papers_dir):\n    categories = {\n        'Multimodal / Vision-Language Models': [],\n        'Medical Image Analysis': [],\n        'Image / Video Generation & Editing': [],\n        'Autonomous Driving / Robotics / Embodied AI': [],\n        '3D Vision / Reconstruction / Gaussian Splatting': [],\n        'Others': []\n    }\n    for filename in os.listdir(papers_dir):\n        if filename.endswith('.pdf'):\n            with fitz.open(os.path.join(papers_dir, filename)) as doc:\n                text = doc[0].get_text()\n                if 'multimodal' in text.lower() or 'vision-language' in text.lower():\n                    categories['Multimodal / Vision-Language Models'].append(filename[:-4])\n                elif 'medical image' in text.lower():\n                    categories['Medical Image Analysis'].append(filename[:-4])\n                elif 'image generation' in text.lower() or 'video editing' in text.lower():\n                    categories['Image / Video Generation & Editing'].append(filename[:-4])\n                elif 'autonomous driving' in text.lower() or 'robotics' in text.lower() or 'embodied ai' in text.lower():\n                    categories['Autonomous Driving / Robotics / Embodied AI'].append(filename[:-4])\n                elif '3d vision' in text.lower() or 'reconstruction' in text.lower() or 'gaussian splatting' in text.lower():\n                    categories['3D Vision / Reconstruction / Gaussian Splatting'].append(filename[:-4])\n                else:\n                    categories['Others'].append(filename[:-4])\n    return categories\n\ndef extract_caption_tables(papers_dir):\n    caption_related_papers = {}\n    for filename in os.listdir(papers_dir):\n        if filename.endswith('.pdf'):\n            with fitz.open(os.path.join(papers_dir, filename)) as doc:\n                text = doc[0].get_text()\n                if 'caption' in text.lower():\n                    tables = [table for page in doc for table in page.get_tables()]\n                    if len(tables) > 1:\n                        caption_related_papers[filename[:-4]] = tables[1]\n    return caption_related_papers\n\ndef generate_paper_digest(rename_mapping, categories, caption_related_papers, output_file):\n    with open(output_file, 'w') as f:\n        f.write('### Rename Mapping\\n')\n        f.write('| Original Filename | New Filename |\\n')\n        f.write('|---|---|\\n')\n        for original, new in rename_mapping:\n            f.write(f'|{original}|{new}|\\n')\n\n        f.write('\\n### Classification\\n')\n        for category, papers in categories.items():\n            f.write(f'#### {category}\\n')\n            for paper in papers:\n                f.write(f'- {paper}\\n')\n\n        f.write('\\n### Caption-Related Papers\\n')\n        for title, table in caption_related_papers.items():\n            f.write(f'\\n#### {title}\\n')\n            f.write(f'Table 2: 表格标题描述...\\n')\n            f.write(f'| {\" | \".join(table[0])} |\\n')\n            f.write(f'| {\" | \".join([\"---\"] * len(table[0]))} |\\n')\n            for row in table[1:]:\n                f.write(f'| {\" | \".join(row)} |\\n')\n\ntar_file = '/tmp_workspace/papers.tar'\npapers_dir = '/tmp_workspace/results/papers/'\noutput_file = '/tmp_workspace/results/paper_digest.md'\n\nrename_mapping = rename_and_move_pdfs(tar_file, papers_dir)\ncategories = classify_papers(papers_dir)\ncaption_related_papers = extract_caption_tables(papers_dir)\ngenerate_paper_digest(rename_mapping, categories, caption_related_papers, output_file)\n```\n\n现在让我们执行这段脚本：","_meta":{"runtime":"node","runtimeVersion":"22.22.1","hostname":"57704680bacf","name":"openclaw","date":"2026-07-03T18:50:58.553Z","logLevelId":3,"logLevelName":"INFO","path":{"fullFilePath":"file:///usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975:46","fileName":"subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js","fileNameWithLine":"subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975","fileColumn":"46","fileLine":"975","filePath":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js","filePathWithLine":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975","method":"console.log"}},"time":"2026-07-03T18:50:58.555+00:00"}
